MANGAZINI YINO yaKaposhi Kakutalila , yeji kuvumbika Yehova Kalunga uze apwa Mwangana mwilu nahamavu .
Yeji kuvendejekanga vatu namujimbu wamwaza wakuvuluka nge Wangana waKalunga wamwilu kalinwomu ukumise upi wosena nakwalumuna kano kaye kupwa palachise .
Yeji kukolezezanga vatu vafwelele Yesu Kulishitu , uze atufwililile mangana tukayoye haya myaka yosena , uze ali jino nakuyula mwaMwangana waWangana waKalunga .
Yino mangazini vanayisonekanga kufuma vene mu 1879 , kaha kayeshi kukundwiza vyamapolitikiko .
Vyuma vyosena vasonekamo vyazama haMbimbiliya .
Bebe azangile chikuma ise .
Mazu kana kawamuvendejekeleko , oloze amwivwishile kukola kumuchima .
Bebe ahanjikilenga mapapa kakavulu ngwenyi , “ Kufwa chatata kachawahileko . ”
Omu mwahichile myaka yayivulu , Bebe asonekele mujimbu wakufwa chaise mumukanda .
Bebe amwene ngwenyi cheji kumbatanga tando yayisuku numba ushona ukeheko chikumanyi nge tunafwisa mutu twazanga chikuma .
MuMbimbiliya , kufwa vachivuluka ngwavo “ muka - kole wakukuminyina . ”
Kufwa cheji kuvatwilako kuyoya chamutu , kaha katwatwama nangolo jakuchihonesako . Kakavulu cheji kwizanga mukukasumuna , nakujiha vatu twazanga .
Vatu vosena veji kwivwanga kukola chikuma kumuchima nge vanafwisa .
Ngocho katwatela kulikomokelako nge natulishona chikuma hakufwisa mutu twazanga .
Pamo munahase kulihulisa ngwenu : ‘ Uno nangukecha kulishona tahi ?
Ngunahase kuvendejeka ngachilihi vakwetu vaze vanafwisa ?
Kutala vatu twazanga vaze vafwa navakayoya cheka tahi ? ’
Uno mwahombaho lyehi mwomwo yakuviza tahi ?
Tutalenu omu kakuluka yetu Apalahama evwile hakufwisa puwenyi .
Mbimbiliya yamba ngwayo “ Apalahama alishonene nakulila Sala . ”
Chasoloka nge “ alishonene ” hatando yayisuku .
Alishonene “ hamakumbi amavulu , ” kaha vaka - tanga yenyi kavahashile kumuvendejekako .
