Omu mukiko nachikapwa nakuli vatu vosena vaze vafwelela ngwavo Kalunga mwakavasangula nakutwama hano hamavu .
Nge nayenu mwafwisaho lyehi mutu mwazanga , pamo vishina vino tunashimutwila kavyeshi kuhasa kukumisa ushona wenu wosenako .
Oloze kushinganyekanga hajishiko jaKalunga jamuMbimbiliya nachimikafwa mupwenga nalutalililo lwamwenemwene nangolo jakumikafwa mumike nge muli nakulishona . — Wavaka - Tesolonyika 1 , 4 : 13 .
Kutala muli nakusaka kutachikiza vyuma vikwavo vyakumikafwa mumike nge muli nakulishona tahi ?
Nyi pamo mweji kuhulisanga vihula vyeka vyakufwana nge chino : “ Mwomwo ika Kalunga etavishila upi nakuyanda ? ”
Yenunga hakeyala yetu ya jw.org , mumone omwo Mbimbiliya yinahase kumivendejeka hakukumbulula vihula vyenu .
“ Kalunga . . . mwakahunda masoji osena kumeso avo , kufwa kacheshi kukapwako chekako . ” — Kusoloka 21 : 3 , 4 .
Uno Kaposhi Kakutalila ali nakushimutwila omwo Kalunga mwakatesamo lushiko kana nomwo natukanganyala .
CHIHANDE CHACHINENE | MWOMWO IKA YESU AYANJILILE NAKUFWA ?
Mumwaka wa 33 C.E . , Yesu wakuNazaleta vamujihile .
Oloze Kalunga amusangwile , kaha omu mwahichile makumbi 40 ayile mwilu .
Mujimbu wakufwa chaYesu vausoneka muMikanda yaMujimbu Wamwaza yiwana yaVisoneka VyachiHelase vyaVaka - Kulishitu , vavuluka ngwavo Tesetamende Yayihya .
Oloze hakuwana nge afwile , vatu vakwononoka vosena vatalilila kukalivwisa kuwaha vyuma avashika Kalunga .
Chikupu vene vihande vyaYesu vasoneka muMikanda yaMujimbu Wamwaza vyapwa vyamuchano .
Vihande vasoneka muMikanda yaMujimbu Wamwaza , vyasolola chikupu nge vyuma kana vyapwile vyamuchano .
Chakutalilaho , vasonekamo majina avihela vize viliko noholyapwa .
Vasonekamo nawa namajina avatu vayoyele halwola kana , vaze vasoneka namumikanda yakukaye yakushikulu . — Luka 3 : 1 , 2 , 23 .
Yesu vamuvuluka namumikanda yakukaye vasonekele kuvatu mulikulukaji lyamyaka lyakulivanga nalyamuchivali .
* Jila vajihililemo Yesu vasoneka muMikanda yaMujimbu Wamwaza yalitombola najila yize vaLoma vajihilililengamo vatu .
Vyuma vyosena vyasolokele vavitavila , kaha vavisoneka nakuli tumbaji twenyi .
Unjiho wosena ou wasolola nge vatu vaze vasonekele mikanda yaMujimbu Wamwaza vapwile vakashishi kaha nawa vasonekele mijimbu yamuchano yaYesu .
Vatu vavavulu vetavila ngwavo Yesu kwapwile kaha nawa afwile , oloze vamwe veji kuhuhwasananga mujimbu wakusanguka chenyi .
Navaposetolo jenyi hakavanga kavetavilile mujimbu wakusanguka chenyiko .
Oloze kuhuhwasana chosena chakumine omu ava vaposetolo natumbaji veka vamwene Yesu kuvihela vyakulisezaseza .
Halwola lumwe , vatu vaze vamwene Yesu hanyima yakusanguka chenyi vapwile kafwe 500 . — Wavaka - Kolinde 1 , 15 : 6 .
Tumbaji vomikile nakwambulula vyakusanguka chaYesu kuli vatu vosena kuhakilako vene navaze vamujihile , numba tuhu kulinga ngocho chahakile myono yavo muponde kaha veka vavakashilenga mutumenga .
Kutala tumbaji vavavulu kachi vomikile nakwambulula nge vatachikijile ngwavo Yesu kasangukileko nyi ?
Enga , kusanguka chaYesu chikiko chalingisa vaka - Kulishitu vatwaleho lika namulimo wavo putu vene kushikulu .
Vyuma vasoneka muMikanda yaMujimbu Wamwaza vyakuvuluka kufwa chaYesu nakusanguka chenyi vyapwa vyamuchano kaha nawa vyamwenemwene .
Kutanga mijimbu kana nachimikafwa mwinjikize ngwenu vyuma kana vyasolokele chikupu .
Lufwelelo lwenu naluzama hakutachikiza ovyo vyalingishile vyuma kana visoloke .
Mutu umwe shina Tacitus uze asemukile mu 55 C.E . , asonekele ngwenyi “ Kulishitu , kuze kwafuma lijina lyavaka - Kulishitu , vamuyanjishile chikuma kuli Pondeu Pilatu uze apwile chilolo muchiyulo chaChivelyu . ”
Yesu vamuvuluka nawa kuli Suetonius ( wamulikulukaji lyamyaka lyakulivanga ) ; nakuli kaYuleya uze alinangwile vyakushikulu Josephus ( wamulikulukaji lyamyaka lyakulivanga ) ; nakuli Pliny wakanyike uze apwile nguvulu wakuMbitunya ( wakumaputukilo alikulukaji lyamyaka lyamuchivali ) .
Mijimbu kana yatela kutukafwa twitavile nakufwelela Yesu .
Kaposetolo Petulu asonekele vyakusanguka chaYesu ngwenyi : “ Kalunga amusangwile halikumbi lyamuchitatu nakumulingisa asoloke , keshi kuli vatu vosenako , oloze kuli vinjiho vaze vatongwele chimweza kuli Kalunga , kuli etu vene , etu twalile nenyi nakunwa nenyi omu alingile hanasanguka lyehi kuvafu . ”
Mujimbu wamumukanda waMateu watulweza ngwawo , omu vaka - kole vevwile ngwavo Yesu nasanguka , valikungulwile nakumutwama punga mangana mujimbu kana uhone kutandakana kuvatu . — Mateu 28 : 11 - 15 .
Uno echi chalumbununa nge Yesu asakile vatu vahone kutachikiza kusanguka chenyi tahi ?
Nduma , Petulu ahanjikile nawa ngwenyi : “ Atulwezele twambulile vatu mujimbu nakuhana unjiho ngwetu , ou ikiye vene uze venyikile kuli Kalunga kupwa muka - kusopesa vavatonyi navafu . ”
Omu mukiko vanalinginga vaka - Kulishitu vamuchano kufuma vene kushikulu nakuheta kumakumbi ano . — Vilinga 10 : 42 .
“ Nge muze shili yengilile mukaye kuhichila muli mutu umwe nakufwa nawa kuhichila mushili . ” — Wavaka - Loma 5 : 12
Vatu vavavulu vanahase kwitavila ngwavo eyo , oloze ngwavo kacheshi kuhashiwako mwomwo vatu vosena veji kufwanga .
Nyi ngachilihi nge vanamihulisa ngwavo , “ Kutala namusaka kufwa tahi ? ”
Vatu vavavulu vanahase kukumbulula ngwavo nduma .
Mbimbiliya yahanjika nge Kalunga atengele vatu namuchima wakusaka kuyoya myaka yosena .
Yahanjika ngwayo , “ Nahake kuyoya chahaya myaka yosena mumichima yavo . ” — Muka - kwambulula 3 : 11 .
Kutala Kalunga alingako vyuma vimwe mangana akumise ukalu kana tahi ?
Mbimbiliya yakumbulula kanawa vihula kana , novyo vyalingishile Yesu ayande nakufwa .
Tupetulu vatatu vakulivanga vamumukanda waKuputuka , vatulweza nge Kalunga akiswile valunga napwevo vakulivanga Alama naEve mangana vayoyenga myaka yosena , navyuma vatela kulinga mangana vayoye myaka yosena .
Tupetulu kana nawa vatulweza ovyo vahonenene kwononoka kuli Kalunga nakujimbalisa kuyoya vavashikile .
Vyuma muka vyafuma hakulikanga chaAlama ?
Hakulikanga chenyi , Alama alingile shili .
Ngachize , kahashile cheka kuyoya myaka yosenako , kaha afwile .
Uno Kalunga nalingiko vyuma vimwe mangana akumise ukalu kana tahi ?
Kalunga awahisa vyuma mangana asokole vatu kuvihuli vize vyeza mwomwo yashili avulumwine Alama . Echi chalingisa vatu vakahase kuyoya myaka yosena .
Mbimbiliya yamba ngwayo : “ Fweto yashili kufwa . ”
Echi chalumbununa nge kufwa cheza mwomwo yashili .
Evi vikiko vyalingisa vatu vosena vafwenga .
Kakweshi mutu mwahasa kuchina kufwako , mwomwo twasemuka nashili .
Oloze Kalunga atumine Mwanenyi Yesu , kwiza nakutusokola ‘ kushili . ’
Kufwa chaYesu chasokolwela vatu jila yakuyoya myaka yosena
Hakuwana nge Alama uze apwile mutu wakukupuka kononokele Kalungako ngocho anehele shili nakufwa , ngachize kwasakiwile mutu wakupuka mangana atusokole kushili kana .
Mbimbiliya yahanjika ngwayo : “ Nge muze vavalingishile vavavulu kupwa vaka - shili hakulikanga chayauze mutu umwe , mukiko nawa munavavalingisa vavavulu kupwa vakwoloka hakwononoka chayauze mutu umwe . ”
Afumine mwilu nakwiza hamavu mwamutu wakukupuka * nakutufwila .
Echi chatulingisa tupwenga nausoko naKalunga nakupwa nalutalililo lwakuyoya myaka yosena .
Mwomwo ika Yesu afwililile ?
Kutala Kalunga Wangolo Josena keshi kahashile kuhanjika kaha ngwenyi vana vaAlama vayoye myaka yosenako tahi ?
Nge Kalunga alumwine elu lushimbi halwola kana , kachi vatu vafwefulula jishimbi jenyi jikwavo .
Uno kachi chinapu chakutamo kuli Kalunga kusakulaho vatu vamwe nakusezaho vakwavo mangana vakayoye myaka yosena tahi ?
Kutala vatu kachi vamumona ngwavo apwa wakwoloka tahi ?
Hakuwana nge Kalunga eji kulinganga mwaya chiyulo chenyi , chatukafwa tufwelele ngwetu mwalinganga lika vyuma vyakwoloka .
Kufwa chaYesu chakulihana ivene , chasokolwela vatu jila yakukayoyela muPalachise hano hamavu myaka yosena .
Yesu ahanjikile mazu vasoneka hali Yowano 3 : 16 ngwenyi : “ Kalunga azangile chikuma kaye ngocho ahanyine Mwanenyi umwe kaha wakulipwila , mangana ngwenyi weshowo mwamufwelela vakahone kumunongesa , oloze akapwe nakuyoya chahaya myaka yosena . ”
Yesu hakulisuula kufwa asolwele nge azanga vatu kaha nawa akundwiza chiyulo chaKalunga .
Mwomwo ika Yesu ayanjilile nakufwa mujila yayipi ngana muze vasoneka muMikanda yaMujimbu Wamwaza ?
Kwononoka nakushishika chenyi muukalu chalingishile afwefulule Liyavolo uze ahanjika ngwenyi vatu kaveshi kuhasa kuzachila Kalungako nge vali muukalu .
Mazu ahanjikile Satana asolokele kupwa amuchano halwola afungulwile Alama .

Oloze Yesu anonokele Kalunga chamokomoko naukalu .
Ngachize , asolwele hatoma nge , naAlama nge asakile , kachi ononokele kuli Kalunga .
Yesu atusela chakutalilaho chamwaza chakwononoka Kalunga chamokomoko navyeseko .
Yesu atulweza vyuma twatela kulinga hakwamba ngwenyi : “ Echi chikiko kuyoya chahaya myaka yosena , kukutachikiza ove Kalunga umwe kaha wamuchano , nayou nawa watumine , Yesu Kulishitu . ” — Yowano 17 : 3 .
Vaka - kusoneka mangazini yino vali nakumilomba mulinangule chikuma vyaKalunga wamuchano Yehova , naMwanenyi Yesu Kulishitu .
Vinjiho jaYehova vamungalila yenu navawahilila kumikafwa .
