Shimbu kanda Yesu afwenga , akungulwile vaposetolo jenyi nakuvalweza vyakwanuka kufwa chenyi .
Ambile ngwenyi : “ Lingenunga lika ngocho mungwanukilengaho ami . ”
Hakusaka kwononoka kulushimbi kana , Vinjiho jaYehova mukaye kosena veji kulikungululanga kamwe mumwaka nakwanuka kufwa chaYesu .
Uno mwaka Kwanuka Kufwa chaYesu nachikapwako lyaChitatu , March 23 , hakulembalemba chalikumbi .
