Nge kumwapwile muIsalele halwola kwapwile Eli navana venyi , kachi mwalingile ngachilihi ?
Eli ahonene ngachilihi kuhuhumuna vana venyi ?
Shili muka yayinene avulumwine Ndavichi , kaha Kalunga alingile ngachilihi ?
( a ) Kaposetolo Petulu ahonene kutesamo ngachilihi mazu enyi ?
( b ) Mwomwo ika Yehova atwalileho lika kuzachisa Petulu okunyi avulumwine ?
Mwomwo ika mwatela kufwelela ngwenu Yehova eji kulinganga vyuma vyakwoloka lwola lwosena ?
Mwomwo ika Yesu ahonene kupihilila havyuma alingile Yuta Isakalyote naPetulu ?
Vyuma muka Mbimbiliya yahanjikile chimweza havangamba jaYehova vamakumbi ano ?
Twatela kumona ngachilihi tutenga twavakwetu ?
13 , 14 . ( a ) Mwomwo ika twatela kutalilila vakwetu chikoki ?
( b ) Vyuma muka vatushika vize twatela kwanukanga ?
Yesu atulweza tulinge vyuma muka nge vakwetu vanalimbenje ?
Vyuma muka munakufwila kulinga nge vakwenu vanamilingi vyavipi ?
( Tangenu Mateu 5 : 23 , 24 . )
Vihula kana kavyeshi vyavikaluko .
Mazu kana apwa amuchano mwomwo Mbimbiliya yatulweza kupwa namangana nakunangakana .
Hali Vishimo 3 : 13 - 15 vamba ngwavo : “ Awahilila mutu uze mwawana mangana , nauze mwaheta uhashi wakukekesa vyuma , kuwana mangana chinawahe kuhambakana kuwana palata , kupwa nawo chinawahe kuhambakana kupwa naulu .
Apwa amalemu kuhambakana malolwa akolale , kaha vyuma vyosena nauzanga kavyeshi kuteseka nawo hamweko . ”
Yesu Kulishitu ahana chakutalilaho chamwaza chakupwa nakashishi .
Hakupwa yami ngwapwile mukulwane haze hakapani , twalikashilenga ‘ chivwasano ’ navaka - kutelesa mitelo nakuvahana majika kanwa mangana vahone kututelesa jimbongo jajivulu .
Ngocho vangutachikijile kupwa ngumutu wakuhona kashishi .
Ngwahana chakutalilaho chamwaza kuli vana vami vavali , kaha vangutongola kuzata milimo muchikungulwilo .
Vatu vaze ngweji kufwetanga mitelo yakapani yami vangumona jino kupwa mutu wakashishi namuchano . ”
Lute ayile kuIsalele kuze akalemeselenga Kalunga wamuchano .
